        <abstract>
            <p>Thanks HTS for his valuable information. Hopes to arrive at probable answer to question of proportion of males to females in the progeny of butterflies bred in domestication.</p>
            <p>On courtship of butterflies, CD believes something more than chance is involved in determining which male is successful.</p>
        </abstract>
